Basic Building Blocks
 1. modulev- To Import 3rd party modules(root modules).
 2. Component - To create html,cssand ts file.


Basic Commands
 1. ng new project_name -(To create a new project).
 2. ng g c Component_name -(To create a new Component).
 3. ng serve --open -(To run Angular file).


A)Basic concept

ts --> component
html-->view


1. Data Binding
      * Share data between components.
      i.one way data binding.(One-direction).
          * ts-->html or html-->ts.

            a. component to view.
              1. string interpolation.
                 SYNTAX:
                   {{Expression}}
              2. property binding
                  SYNTAX:
                    [atrribute name]="property"

            b. View to component
              2. Event binding
                SYNTAX:
                (event_name)="function_name"

              2.1) Event Binding using $event
                SYNTAX:
                (event_name)="function_name($event)"


     ii.two way data binding.(Two-direction).

